立即，[+ chancellor +] 着手建设「苏维埃德国」：尽可能将权力集中于共产党，清洗国家机构中的反共分子，并派遣街头武装攻击「人民公敌」。

@thalmann_war
on-arrival: nazi_rebel = 1; foreign_minister_party = "SPD"; interior_minister_party = "SPD"; justice_minister_party = "SPD"; labor_minister_party = "SPD"; reichswehr_minister_party = "SPD"; economic_minister_party = "SPD"; finance_minister_party = "SPD"; agriculture_minister_party = "SPD"; kpd_relation = 80

面对 [+ chancellor +] 出任总理，右翼力量几乎立即发动政变企图。钢盔团与纳粹党冲锋队的部队进入柏林，立刻与我们的支持者发生冲突！国防军内的反动军官率部离营，加入钢盔团阻止共产党夺取权力。无论是否情愿，我们都被迫与共产党并肩作战。

- @civil_war

@thalmann_no_war
on-arrival: coup_progress += 5; leverage = ((spd_r/(spd_r+kpd_r))*kpd_relation); reformist_dissent += 5; neorevisionist_dissent += 5; z_relation -= 10; rfb_strength += 100; rb_strength -= 50; kpd_relation -= 10; kpd_influence += 3; foreign_minister_party = "KPD"; interior_minister_party = "KPD"; justice_minister_party = "KPD"; labor_minister_party = "KPD"; reichswehr_minister_party = "KPD"; economic_minister_party = "KPD"; finance_minister_party = "KPD"; agriculture_minister_party = "KPD";
