中央党（含 [+ bvp_name +]）、德国人民党、德国国家人民党和保守派小党的选票已足以组建右翼联合政府。

@no_right_coalition
go-to: no_majority

然而，德国国家人民党及其领袖胡根贝格拒绝与中央党的「十一月罪人」组建联合。因此，国会大厦无路可达多数。



@right_coalition_2
view-if: right_coalition_failed != 1 and right_coalition >= 50
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 0; spd_toleration = 0; chancellor = "Brüning"; chancellor_party = "Z"; foreign_minister_party = "DVP"; interior_minister_party = "Z"; justice_minister_party = "Z"; labor_minister_party = "Z"; reichswehr_minister_party = "I"; economic_minister_party = "Z"; finance_minister_party = "Z"; agriculture_minister_party = "Z"; in_right_coalition = 1; workers_spd -= 3; new_middle_spd -= 2; judicial_reform -= 1; reichswehr_loyalty -= 0.05; interior_police_loyalty -= 0.05; welfare -= 1; budget += 1; nationalism += 6
