on-arrival: chancellor = "Wirth"; chancellor_party = "Z"; spd_in_government = 0; spd_toleration = 1; z_relation += 5; foreign_minister_party = "DVP"; interior_minister_party = "Z"; justice_minister_party = "I"; labor_minister_party = "Z"; reichswehr_minister_party = "I"; economic_minister_party = ddp_name; finance_minister_party = "DVP"; agriculture_minister_party = "Z"; pro_republic -= 2;

我们支持由中央党在维尔特总理领导下组建的少数派政府。



@no_majority_papen
on-arrival: pro_republic -= 10; next_election_time = time+3; next_election_month = month + 3; next_election_year = year; next_election_year += 1 if next_election_month > 12; next_election_month -= 12 if next_election_month > 12; no_majority_papen_elections += 1; nazi_peak = 1; nazi_peak_timer = 2; nazi_peak_timer += (nsdap_votes/5); workers_ndap -= 6; new_middle_nsdap -= 6; old_middle_nsdap -= 6; rural_nsdap -= 6; unemployed_nsdap -= 6; workers_nsdap -= 3 if largest_party == "NSDAP"; unemployed_nsdap -= 3 if largest_party == "NSDAP"; old_middle_nsdap -= 3 if largest_party == "NSDAP"; new_middle_nsdap -= 3 if largest_party == "NSDAP"; rural_nsdap -= 3 if largest_party == "NSDAP";
go-to: papen_second_term if papen_two_term

选举后，帕彭仍极不受欢迎，毫无联合支持的迹象。针对他的不信任投票几乎立即被发起。无论我们如何投票，该议案都将通过。国会大厦再次被解散。

新选举定于 [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +] 举行。[? if largest_party == "NSDAP" : 尽管纳粹党成为最大党，但他们未能组阁，运动失去势头，把空间让给共产党和德国国家人民党。 ?]

纳粹拒绝支持帕彭政府，引发其极右翼基本盘的困惑与失望。

@papen_second_term
on-arrival: judicial_reform -= 2 if judicial_reform >= 2; reichswehr_loyalty -= 0.05; workers_dnvp += 2; new_middle_dnvp += 5; old_middle_dnvp += 6; rural_dnvp += 6; catholics_dnvp += 3; sh_strength += 50; workers_spd -= 3; workers_kpd -= 3; unemployed_kpd -= 2; dvp_relation -= 5;

帕彭利用这段时间在兴登堡的同意下颁布一道道法令，将其德国国家人民党的主要支持者推回反动政治的前台，并瓦解了我们在全国各地的民主改革成果。

@no_majority_papen_2
on-arrival: chancellor = "Schleicher"; pro_republic -= 10; next_election_time = time+5; next_election_month = month + 5; next_election_year = year; next_election_year += 1 if next_election_month > 12; next_election_month -= 12 if next_election_month > 12; finance_minister_party = "I"; interior_minister_party = "I"; economic_minister_party = "I"; labor_minister_party = "I"; foreign_minister_party = "I"; agriculture_minister_party = "I"; reichswehr_minister = "I";

无组建多数政府的途径。兴登堡对帕彭感到不满，要求其辞职。如今，前陆军将军库尔特·冯·施莱谢尔被任命为总理，同样作为总统制政府的一部分。

施莱谢尔的政府在国会大厦各党中极不受欢迎。尽管他支持与纳粹党组建联合，纳粹却想独揽权力，不愿与施莱谢尔分享。[? if largest_party == "NSDAP" : 然而，纳粹再次未能组阁，进一步丧失势头。 ?]

新选举定于 [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +] 举行。


@no_majority_schleicher
subtitle: 兴登堡将任命谁替代他？
on-arrival: schleicher_times += 1
view-if: schleicher_support < 50 and (spd_support_schleicher or spd_refused_schleicher) and (ddp_support_schleicher or ddp_name == "DDP" or pro_republic >= 40) and (z_support_schleicher or z_party_leader == "Stegerwald" or pro_republic >= 50 or (unemployed <= 30 and reichskonkordat)) and (dvp_support_schleicher or pro_republic >= 55 or nationalism >= 55) and (dnvp_support_schleicher or (spd_support_schleicher and not dnvp_reform and not sapd_formed))
go-to: hitler_chancellor if schleichers_scheme_success or largest_party == "NSDAP" or schleicher_times > 1; schleicher_second_try if not schleichers_scheme_success and largest_party != "NSDAP" and schleicher_times <= 1

@schleicher_second_try

选举之后，仍无明显多数。库尔特·冯·施莱谢尔总理声称有一项拯救德国的计划，并向社民党人发出了模糊的承诺。他声称，为了执政，必须暂时中止国会大厦以防止纳粹党和共产党干扰政府运作，这实际上将给予他和兴登堡独裁权力。

[? if works_program <= 0: 工会对施莱谢尔的计划略有好感，因为他们认为施莱谢尔的经济计划与 ADGB 的 WTB 计划（债务融资的就业创造方案）有共通之处。然而，我党其余部分则强烈反对施莱谢尔。 ?]

有传言称施莱谢尔也以类似的合作承诺接近纳粹党；他似乎认为自己能「驯服」纳粹。我党多数人不相信他不会让纳粹掌权。此外，与他合作实际上意味着我们「民主」政党身份的终结。

# if this works: delay elections by 1 year (requires over 50% support - need Z and DVP and others to join as well based on relations; DNVP might support? Also should depend on Hindenburg relations).

