@bruning_oppo
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 0; spd_toleration = 0; chancellor = "Brüning"; chancellor_party = "Z"; foreign_minister_party = "DVP"; interior_minister_party = "Z"; justice_minister_party = "Z"; labor_minister_party = "Z"; reichswehr_minister_party = "I"; economic_minister_party = "Z"; finance_minister_party = "Z"; agriculture_minister_party = "Z"; grand_coalition_failed = 1

通过拒绝加入或容忍大联合，我们实际上将政府的天平推向右翼。[? if right_coalition >= 50 : 有足够的选票组建包括德国国家人民党在内的右翼联合。然而，德国国家人民党领袖胡根贝格反对与中央党的「十一月罪人」组建联合。当然，纳粹党无意参与联合政府。这意味着不会有足够的选票组建多数联合。 ?][? if right_coalition < 50 : 没有足够的选票组建包括德国国家人民党在内的右翼联合，而德国国家人民党反正也不愿与中央党的「十一月罪人」联合。当然，纳粹党无意参与联合政府。这意味着无路可达多数联合。 ?]

如果我们甚至不「容忍」政府，几个月后将举行新选举。其间，总统和总理可援引宪法第 48 条赋予的紧急权力，基本上以法令执政。而且我们能否在下次选举中表现更好完全不明朗。

- @join_bruning: 加入布吕宁联合。
- @toleration_bruning: 我们终究将容忍布吕宁。
- @brauns_dilemma
- @new_elections: 那就新选举吧！


@new_elections
view-if: neo_weimar_coalition >= 50
on-arrival: {!
Q.marx_relation -= 10;
Q.next_election_month = Q.month + 3;
Q.next_election_time = Q.time + 3;
if (Q.next_election_month > 12) {
    Q.next_election_month -= 12;
    Q.next_election_year = Q.year + 1;
} else {
    Q.next_election_year = Q.year;
}
if (Q.chancellor == "Brüning") {
    Q.z_relation -= 5;
    Q.dvp_relation -= 5;
}
Q.pro_republic -= 4;
Q.new_middle_spd -= 3;
Q.old_middle_spd -= 3;
Q.rural_spd -= 3;
Q.catholics_spd -= 2;
Q.new_middle_dvp -= 5;
Q.old_middle_dvp -= 5;
Q.new_middle_ddp -= 5;
Q.old_middle_ddp -= 5;
Q.rural_dnvp -= 4;
Q.workers_nsdap += 3;
Q.old_middle_nsdap += 5;
Q.new_middle_nsdap += 5;
Q.rural_nsdap += 5;
Q.unemployed_nsdap += 3;
// Thresholds are kind of arbitrary - adjusted because of negative economic effects on pro_republic
if (Q.pro_republic < 45 && Q.pro_republic >= 36) {
    Q.workers_spd -= 2;
}
if (Q.pro_republic < 36 && Q.left_strength < 50) {
    // TODO: if you pursue a consistently revolutionary course, you might avoid this? But you might also cause a coalition between Hitler and the Center.
    Q.z_relation -= 5;
    Q.dvp_relation -= 5;
    Q.ddp_relation -= 3;
    Q.workers_spd -= 3;
    Q.unemployed_spd -= 3;
    Q.new_middle_spd -= 5
    Q.old_middle_spd -= 6;
    Q.rural_spd -= 6;
    Q.catholics_spd -= 3;
    Q.workers_nsdap += 3;
    Q.old_middle_nsdap += 6;
    Q.new_middle_nsdap += 6;
    Q.rural_nsdap += 6;
    Q.unemployed_nsdap += 4;
}
if (Q.left_strength >= 50) {
    Q.z_relation -= 8;
    Q.dvp_relation -= 8;
    Q.ddp_relation -= 4;
    Q.new_middle_nsdap += 4;
    Q.old_middle_nsdap += 6;
    Q.rural_nsdap += 6;
    Q.rural_dnvp += 2;
    Q.rural_dvp -= 4;
    Q.old_middle_dvp -= 4;
    Q.new_middle_dvp -= 4;
    Q.new_middle_ddp -= 2;
    Q.old_middle_other -= 2;
    Q.rural_other -= 2;
    Q.new_middle_other -= 2;
    Q.sa_militancy += 0.01;
    Q.workers_spd += Q.radicalization;
    Q.unemployed_spd += Q.radicalization;
    Q.old_middle_spd -= Q.radicalization;
    Q.rural_spd -= Q.radicalization;
    Q.pro_republic -= 4;
    Q.unemployed_kpd += Q.strife;
    Q.unemployed_nsdap -= Q.strife;
    Q.coup_progress += Q.political_crisis_progress;
}
if (Q.far_right_coalition >= 50) {
    Q.sa_strength += 100;
    Q.sh_strength += 100;
    Q.coup_progress += 3;
}
if (Q.no_majority_elections >= 2) {
    Q.political_crisis_progress += 1
}
!}

无可行的国会大厦多数或少数派政府。下次选举定于 [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +] 举行。

人民对民主的信心在此次磨难中受到动摇。当然，纳粹党正利用这种不稳定来宣称民主不可行，并称德国需要一个强人领袖。

[? if left_strength >= 50 : 资产阶级选民和金融支持者越来越多地转向纳粹党，将其视为防范潜在社会主义革命的捍卫者，但因此纳粹党在工人阶级中的支持有所减少。 ?]

